*''[[Angels Fall]]'' (1983)
*''[[Burn This]]'' (1986)
*''Redwood Curtain'' (1992)
*''A Sense of Place'' (1996)
*''Sympathetic Magic'' (1998)
*''Book of Days'' (2000)
*''Rain Dance'' (2002)
{{col-end}}

